          "title": "GOOGLE LAUNCHES BARD",
          "summary": "It's here! Google’s long anticipated entry into the language models as a service game. Bard is a lightweight version of Lambda, which was a 70B parameter conversational agent trained a few years ago. They have spent a lot of effort making things safe and grounded in truthfulness, we’ll see when people start getting added to the waitlist if it lives up to the promises!",
